  "original_title": "TNA \u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7 - CWC \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "TNA to Dallas - CWC to Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been decided to give the support of the Dravida National Alliance to Member of Parliament Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma in the election to be held in Parliament today for the election of a new President.",
        "This decision was taken in a discussion held yesterday between the members of that party, Mr. Sajith Premadasa and Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma.",
        "Thus, all the 10 members of parliament of the Dravida National Alliance are going to vote for Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma.",
        "Meanwhile, Mr. Jeevan Thondaman says that the Ceylon Labor Congress has decided to support the Acting Prime Minister Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe."
      ],
